{"content":"---\ntitle: \"<system.serviceModel.activation>\"\nms.date: \"03/30/2017\"\nms.assetid: c0cae85f-56cb-4030-8807-6f96edff8d2d\n---\n# \\<system.serviceModel.activation>\nThis configuration section represents the configuration settings for the SMSvcHost.exe tool. The configuration elements can be configured in the SMSvcHost.exe.config file. Specifically, it includes all machine-wide settings that must be configured.  \n  \n## Sample Configuration File  \n The following is a sample configuration file (SMSvcHost.exe.config), which is used by the listener process SMSvcHost.exe.  \n  \n```xml  \n<configuration>\n  <runtime>\n    <gcConcurrent enabled=\"false\" />\n  </runtime>\n  <system.serviceModel.activation>\n    <net.tcp listenBacklog=\"10\"\n             maxPendingAccepts=\"2\"\n             maxPendingConnections=\"100\"\n             receiveTimeout=\"00:00:10\"\n             teredoEnabled=\"false\">\n      <allowAccounts>\n        <!-- LocalSystem account -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-18\"/>\n        <!-- LocalService account -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-19\"/>\n        <!-- Network Service account -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-20\"/>\n        <!-- Administrators account -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-32-544\" />\n        <!-- IIS_IUSRS account (Vista only) -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-32-568\"/>\n      </allowAccounts>\n    </net.tcp>\n    <net.pipe maxConnectionsPendingDispatch=\"100\"\n              maxPendingAccepts=\"2\"\n              receiveTimeout=\"00:00:10\">\n      <allowAccounts>\n        <!-- LocalSystem account -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-18\" />\n        <!-- LocalService account -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-19\" />\n        <!-- Network Service account -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-20\" />\n        <!-- Administrators account -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-32-544\" />\n        <!-- IIS_IUSRS account (Vista only) -->\n        <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-32-568\" />\n      </allowAccounts>\n    </net.pipe>\n    <diagnostics performanceCountersEnabled=\"true\" />\n  </system.serviceModel.activation>\n</configuration>\n```  \n  \n## See also\n\n- <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activation.Configuration>\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,116],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"<system.serviceModel.activation>\"\nms.date: \"03/30/2017\"\nms.assetid: c0cae85f-56cb-4030-8807-6f96edff8d2d","nodes":[{"content":"<system.serviceModel.activation>","nodes":[{"pos":[0,32],"content":"<system.serviceModel.activation>","nodes":[{"content":"&lt;system.serviceModel.activation&gt;","pos":[0,32],"source":"<system.serviceModel.activation>"}]}],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[123,156],"content":"\\<system.serviceModel.activation>","linkify":"\\<system.serviceModel.activation>","nodes":[{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>system.serviceModel.activation&gt;","pos":[0,33],"source":"\\<system.serviceModel.activation>"}]},{"content":"This configuration section represents the configuration settings for the SMSvcHost.exe tool.","pos":[157,249]},{"content":"The configuration elements can be configured in the SMSvcHost.exe.config file.","pos":[250,328]},{"content":"Specifically, it includes all machine-wide settings that must be configured.","pos":[329,405]},{"pos":[414,439],"content":"Sample Configuration File","linkify":"Sample Configuration File","nodes":[{"content":"Sample Configuration File","pos":[0,25]}]},{"content":"The following is a sample configuration file (SMSvcHost.exe.config), which is used by the listener process SMSvcHost.exe.","pos":[443,564]},{"pos":[2122,2130],"content":"See also","linkify":"See also","nodes":[{"content":"See also","pos":[0,8]}]}]}